== About ==

User Tagging is a MediaWiki extension that allows for @-style tagging of
usernames, using autocompletion. If you enter an '@' in any textarea,
entering any additional characters will begin autocompletion, and the
autocompletion will continue until a username is selected, or there are
no more possible matches, 

== Authors ==

This extension was created by Yaron Koren.
